Very frustrating that there doesn&#39;t appear to be any documentation describing that `SessionFactoryBuilderFactory` no longer works.  Well, if there is, I wasn&#39;t able to find it.  What I did find was [TypeContributor](https://docs.jboss.org/hibernate/orm/current/userguide/html_single/Hibernate_User_Guide.html#basic-type-contributor).  

Based my change, I think the following would work for you.

    public class CustomTypeContributor implements TypeContributor {

      @Override
      public void contribute(TypeContributions typeContributions, ServiceRegistry serviceRegistry) {
        typeContributions.contributeJavaType(new MonetaryAmountType());
      }
    }

Just as with `CustomTypeRegistration`, you will need to register `CustomTypeContributor` using service locator.

